    "privileged_info_summary": "The version_diff_highlighter task creates a synthetic dataset with 10 products in 2 spreadsheet versions (ODS format). Exactly 6 cells differ between Version 1 and Version 2: P1001 price (24.99→27.99), P1003 price (45.00→49.99), P1004 quantity (120→135), P1006 name (Webcam HD→HD Webcam), P1008 category (Accessories→Office Supplies), and P1009 price (15.99→17.99). The task requires highlighting these 6 cells in Version 2 with background color. Pass criteria: F1 score ≥0.80 (requiring both Recall ≥0.80 and Precision ≥0.80). Verification uses XML parsing of the ODS file to detect background colors. Ground truth is stored in JSON format with hardcoded fallback in the verifier. Task timeout is 180 seconds, max 15 steps, medium difficulty, sparse reward type.",
